title: The-Laura-Ingraham-Show-PodcastJune 24 2016
description:
Laura Ingraham June 24, 2016  MP3

Nile Gardiner - Director of The Heritage Foundation's Margaret Thatcher Center for Freedom; Frm. Special Advisor to Lady Thatcher "As part of the EU you have no control over people coming in from other EU countries" Jim Roberts - Research Fellow For Economic Freedom and Growth, The Heritage Foundation on Britain vote "it is the people speaking" Roger Simon - Co-Founder of PJ Media on Britain vote "the message is so big" 

The Brexit Wake-Up Call: The Establishment gets their comeuppance, the people finally get their freedom

Lifezette - Laura Ingraham
By voting to leave the European Union, the British people have retaken control of their destiny from an out-of-touch collection of elites who had presided over one disaster after another, and that were anxious to see Britain lose its status as an independent country - something the British have not only cherished, but have often fought to preserve. By doing so, they have not only regained their own freedom, but have sent an important message to elites and Establishment leaders everywhere - including the United States.
